  "courseObjectives": [
    "List out the various steps involved in forensic readiness planning",
    "Comprehend the Code of ethics that an Investigator needs to follow while implementing computer forensics",
    "Analyze file systems and recover deleted files",
    "Explain the process of finding evidences from Windows and Linux operating systems",
    "Analyze system events and network traffic logs",
    "Examine logs to determine attack signatures, identify the nature of the attacks, etc.",
    "Scan an executable file and verify if it has malicious components by performing a thorough analysis of the file",
    "Write a perfect forensic investigation report that meets the needs of all stakeholders"
